  <sub>s</sub> and starting from an initial and complex WP |ψ
  <sub>0</sub> &gt; = |
  <span class="italic">a</span>
  <sub>0</sub> &gt; +
  <span class="italic">i</span>|
  <span class="italic">b</span>
  <sub>0</sub> &gt; (Gray and Balint-Kurti, 
  <a rid="B25" ref-type="bibr" href="#B25">1998</a>). This initial WP describes the entrance channel He
  <span class="sup">+</span>(
  <span class="sup">2</span>
  <span class="italic">S</span>)+H
