     <span class="mn">2</span>
    </div>
    <span class="mo">,</span>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">where (1) and (2) are the diabatic electronic states, 
  <span class="italic">v</span>′, 
  <span class="italic">j</span>′, and 
  <span class="italic">K</span>′ label open vibrational, rotational, and helicity states of the products, respectively, and 
  <span class="bold">
   <span class="italic">S</span>
  </span>
  <span class="sup">
   <span class="italic">J</span>
  </span> is the state-to-state parity adapted 
  <span class="italic">S</span>-matrix at 
  <span class="italic">J</span>. The total ICS is then defined by
 </p>
 <div id="E8" class="disp-formula" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <span class="label">(8)</span>
  <div id="M55" class="math">
   <div class="mrow">
    <div class="msub">
